<L>__{exterior roof day}
<A>__{lieutenant strozah surveys the street traffic. nico, jackson and lukich the two men, dressed as meat processors in hard hats and bloody white coats, rake cattle guts under the eave of a packing plant. jackson, dressed like a usda inspector and carrying a clipboard, inspects a few hanging carcasses.}
